Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.66,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:225788,227665}Or something like that.{NOTE:な～んて言っていたが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:51.16,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:228374,231169}Yes, it was already pretty serious back then.{NOTE:あのころもすでに研究ロスでしたが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:57.00,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:231169,237008}But I still had some hope left\Nwhile I searched for new research themes.{NOTE:心の底では新しい研究テーマを探し求めていたからまだよかったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.09,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:237633,239093}But now…{NOTE:なのに今は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.76,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:239719,242764}Even though I've always believed in the power of science…{NOTE:あれだけ科学の力を信じていたのに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.26,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:243139,244265}Huh…{NOTE:ハァ～…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:08.77,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:244891,248770}Every day he went to the laboratory, and just sighed.{NOTE:研究室にはいるものの毎日ため息ばかり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.98,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:249979,251981}Um, excuse me, Doctor.{NOTE:あのう博士。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.19,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:251981,254192}How is the research going today…?{NOTE:今日も研究は…？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.40,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:254192,256402}Research, huh…?{NOTE:研究か…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.27,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:256402,258279}How nostalgic.{NOTE:懐かしいなぁ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:22.99,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:258988,262992}What have I even been researching about these days?{NOTE:あのころの私は何を目的に研究していたのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:28.33,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:263868,268331}I can't remember even that, Itsy-Bits.{NOTE:それさえももう思い出せないよ、イチビッツ君。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.16,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:268331,269165}Eh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:33.92,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:269165,273920}But… Doctor, you always said that there's nothing impossible for science.{NOTE:で…でも博士はいつも科学に不可能はないって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:34.58,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:273920,274587}Hmph.{NOTE:フッ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:37.21,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:274587,277215}Why did I say such a thing…?{NOTE:そんなこと言ったっけなぁ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.59,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:277215,279592}It's already a story of the past.{NOTE:もう過去の話だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:40.67,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:279592,280676}Eh…{NOTE:ハァ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.51,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:280676,281511}Huh?{NOTE:えっ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:48.55,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:282303,288559}The Doctor has completely lost his motivation for research and his purpose in life.{NOTE:博士は今や研究はもちろん人生の目的も完全に見失っているのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.43,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:288559,290436}That Manelger?{NOTE:あのマネルガーが？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.64,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:290436,291646}You don't say.{NOTE:ふ～む。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.43,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:291646,293439}That sucks.{NOTE:それは大変だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:56.06,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:293439,296067}Yes! It sucks a lot!{NOTE:はい！大変なので～す！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.06,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:296067,297068}Like I care!{NOTE:な～んて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:59.32,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:297068,299320}Did you think Navirou believed you for even a second?{NOTE:ﾅﾋﾞﾙｰが信じると思うか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.27,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:299320,300279}Huh?{NOTE:へっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.69,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:300279,302698}I can't believe it at all.{NOTE:全然信じられないゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.24,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:302698,304242}{NOTE:ふわわ～…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:07.28,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:304242,307286}I got somewhat sleepy-nyaa.{NOTE:何だか眠くなっちゃったでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.74,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:307286,309747}Good night.{NOTE:おやすみなしゃい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:10.91,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:309747,310915}Hey!{NOTE:ちょっと～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.79,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:310915,312792}Please don't go to sleep!{NOTE:寝ないでくださいよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.25,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:312792,315253}You're the ones who modified him to do that!{NOTE:お前たちがそう改造したんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.92,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:315253,316921}A-Anyway…{NOTE:と、とにかく…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:20.84,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:316921,320842}With the Doctor being like this,\NI have no idea what to do from now on…{NOTE:博士が今のままでは僕もこの先どうしたらいいか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.13,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:322009,324136}So please help me.{NOTE:どうか助けてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.68,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:324136,326681}Please believe me!{NOTE:僕を信じてください！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:33.22,Default,Cryo,1,1,0,,{TIME:326681,333229}Believe you? How can we, when the trust between us and the two of you doesn't span even a single millimeter?{NOTE:信じるも何もそもそもわれわれとあなた方の間に信頼など１ミリもありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.94,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:333229,336941}We're not obligated to help you.{NOTE:故に助ける義理も一切ないということです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.06,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:336941,339068}So cruel and cool…{NOTE:残酷なほどクール…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.19,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:339068,342196}Like I said, you modified him so!{NOTE:だから！お前らがそう改造したんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.24,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:342196,344240}Don't make me say it over and over!{NOTE:何度も言わせるな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.24,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:344240,345241}Oh!{NOTE:あっ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.32,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:345241,347326}That's right!{NOTE:そ、そうなのです！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.82,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:347326,349829}Everyone here was modified by the Doctor.{NOTE:皆さんは博士に改造された。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:56.54,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:350663,356544}In other words, you owe your solid bond to the Doctor!{NOTE:つまり、博士はあなた方の固い絆を作った生みの親なので～す！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:57.79,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:356544,357795}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:01.34,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:357795,361340}Now, let's all get Dr. Manelger motivated again!{NOTE:さあ、みんなでマネルガー博士を盛り上げましょう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.17,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:361340,363175}Don't joke like that.{NOTE:冗談じゃない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:07.84,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:363175,367847}Besides, Navirou is already busy saving Avinia!{NOTE:それにナビルーたちは今アユリアを救うのが何より先決だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:11.43,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:367847,371434}We have no time to deal with you.{NOTE:あなたたちの相手をしてる暇なんてないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:17.10,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:371434,377106}Oh, by the way, it seems that the Doctor has obtained information where Avinia is being held…{NOTE:あっ、そういえば博士アユリアさんの居場所がどうのこうの言っていたような…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.23,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:377106,378232}What!?{NOTE:何っ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:23.27,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:378232,383279}Well, the last time we met the Doctor,\Nhe did know about the Ebon Riders…{NOTE:確かにこの間会ったときも博士はﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞのことを知っていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.48,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:383279,384488}Right, right?{NOTE:でしょでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:30.32,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:384488,390328}If you help the Doctor's get back on his feet,\NI'm sure he'll be able to help you!{NOTE:博士の元気を取り戻せばきっと貴重な情報を聞き出せるに違いありませ～ん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.12,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:391370,393122}Now, O' great Numbers!{NOTE:さあ、ナンバーズの皆さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:38.04,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:393122,398044}Let's cheer up your creator, Dr. Manelger, together!{NOTE:みんなの生みの親マネルガー博士を元気づけに一緒に参りましょう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:42.29,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:400087,402298}This is the place. Over there!{NOTE:あっ！皆さん。あそこで～す！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:50.30,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:406844,410306}First of all, you're hungry, aren't you?{NOTE:取りあえず、皆さん。おなかがすいたでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:53.47,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:410306,413476}Before seeing the Doctor, we'll have a welcome lunch.{NOTE:博士に会う前にウエルカムランチでも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:57.81,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:413476,417813}Of course, we have a special donut for Mr. Navirou.{NOTE:もちろん、ナビルーさんにはスペシャルドーナツをご用意しておりま～す。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.81,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:418481,420816}A special donut!?{NOTE:スペシャルドーナツ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:09.95,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:425363,429951}It was hard to make a donut of this size.{NOTE:この大きさのドーナツを作るのは大変だったんですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:13.99,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:429951,433996}It truly is a special donut,\Nmade with great craftsmanship.{NOTE:まさに職人技のスペシャルドーナツです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.12,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:433996,436123}Thank you for the food!{NOTE:いっただっきまーす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.34,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:446842,448344}Actually…{NOTE:実は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:33.55,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:448344,453557}Since the Doctor's hasn't been researching anything,\Nour income is at zero these days.{NOTE:博士の研究が何も進まないのでただ今収入ゼロでして…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.81,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:457311,459814}This is our welcome lunch…?{NOTE:何がウエルカムランチよ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.44,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:459814,462441}Balloon donuts, huh…?{NOTE:風船ドーナツだゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:46.27,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:462441,466278}So where is Manelger and what's he up to?{NOTE:それでマネルガーは今どこで何をしている？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:48.78,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:466278,468781}I think he's in the laboratory.{NOTE:たぶん研究室かと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:51.90,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:468781,471909}Or rather, former laboratory…{NOTE:いや、元研究室と言うべきか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.49,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:471909,473494}"I think"!?{NOTE:たぶんって！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.66,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:473494,476664}You don't even know what your boss is doing!{NOTE:お前らは相手が何をしているのか分からないような…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.20,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:476664,479208}Do you have that thin of a relationship?{NOTE:…薄～い関係だったのか!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.96,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:479208,481961}No, that's…{NOTE:いや、そういうわけでは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:02.79,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:481961,482795}Hmph.{NOTE:フッ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:07.09,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:482795,487091}Compared to that, me and Cheval are perfect!{NOTE:それに比べて僕とシュヴァルさんは完璧です！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:11.38,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:487091,491387}And I'm doing pretty good working with Nariki!{NOTE:俺だってナリキと力を合わせて頑張っているところだぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:14.97,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:491387,494974}I love Mille-Mille-nyaa.{NOTE:僕はミルミルが大好きでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:18.31,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:494974,498310}I am a good match with Hyoro as well.{NOTE:僕だってヒョロさんと息ぴったりゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:21.10,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:498310,501105}Navirou and Lute won't lose either!{NOTE:ナビルーとリュートだって負けないぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.10,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:501105,503107}For example, when there is only one donut left…{NOTE:ドーナツが一つしかないときも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:29.98,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:505234,509989}Navirou always thinks to share it with Lute!{NOTE:ナビルーは必ず一度はリュートに半分分けてやろうかと考えてから！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.45,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:510740,512450}(But then I eat it myself anyways.){NOTE:全部一人で食べている！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.24,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:513784,516245}So you don't share it with him after all?{NOTE:って結局分けてないゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.66,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:516245,519665}It's the thought that counts!{NOTE:気持ちだけはいつだってリュートと半分こだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:45.50,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:520708,525504}I trust and respect the Doctor, too.{NOTE:僕だって博士を信頼していますし尊敬しています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:49.96,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:525504,529967}But he's so closed off to everything now.{NOTE:でも博士は今全てに対し心を閉ざしているんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:54.09,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:529967,534096}That's why, as his assistant for many years…{NOTE:だから長年博士の助手を務めた僕にも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:59.51,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:534096,539518}It only tells you what kind of bond there was between you and the Doctor.{NOTE:つまりあなたと博士はしょせんその程度の絆だったってことです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.02,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:539518,541020}I feel sorry for you.{NOTE:残念でしたね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.68,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:541020,542688}W-Wrong!{NOTE:ち、違います！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:06.65,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:542688,546650}The Doctor and I are connected by bonds of research.{NOTE:僕と博士は研究という絆でつながっていたんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:10.40,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:546650,550404}So if he regains his motivation again…{NOTE:だから博士がもう一度やる気を取り戻せば…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:12.57,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:550404,552573}Whatever, enough with the talking!{NOTE:お前らの話はどうでもいい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.03,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:552573,555034}The important thing is that I'm still hungry…{NOTE:それよりおなかがすいた～…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.20,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:556118,557203}I know.{NOTE:そうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:23.37,Default,Navirou,1,1,0,,{TIME:557203,563375}I can summon the smell of donuts thanks to the Navirou Burst Fart I acquired with the Rite of Channeling.{NOTE:こういうときは伝承の儀で身に付けたナビルーバーストプープでドーナツの香りだけでも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:25.12,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:563375,565127}Anything but that!{NOTE:それは駄目～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.79,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:565669,568798}Then what should I do about my hunger?!{NOTE:じゃあこの空腹をどうしろっていうんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.88,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:568798,570883}Is there any food in here?!{NOTE:どこかに食べ物はないのか!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.51,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:575429,576514}Manelger!{NOTE:マネルガー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.80,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:576847,578808}Buh? Bwe?{NOTE:ばう？ぶふ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.89,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:578808,579892}Donuts!{NOTE:ドーナツだ…}
