Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:57.33,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:894915,897334}But sometimes a blunder can't be avoided.{NOTE:時には失敗することもあるだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:01.96,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:898210,901964}The researcher doesn't need to take responsibility for those, though.{NOTE:だがその責任を取る必要は研究者にはない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.34,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:901964,903340}What the heck!?{NOTE:ふざけるな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:07.30,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:903340,907302}Do you have any idea how many people you've troubled with your research!?{NOTE:お前の研究のせいでどれだけの人に迷惑が掛かったと…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:12.47,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:907302,912474}But instead, the researcher can be challenged to do anything!{NOTE:だがその代わり研究者は何度でもチャレンジするものだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:15.14,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:914143,915144}Doctor…?{NOTE:博士…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.97,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:915144,916979}Trouble-nyaa!{NOTE:大変でしゅニャ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:22.60,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:916979,922609}The remodeled Tigrex appeared again and is causing chaos everywhere-nyaa!{NOTE:改造ティガレックスがまた現れたって向こうで大騒ぎになってるでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.27,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:922609,924278}What!?{NOTE:何だって!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:25.65,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:924278,925654}Don't worry.{NOTE:安心しろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.53,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:925654,927531}We still have this.{NOTE:わしにはこれがある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.07,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:927531,929074}Eh? Doctor!{NOTE:えっ？博士！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.32,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:929074,931326}You mean, we still had it?{NOTE:それまだ取ってあったんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:36.62,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:931326,936623}Researchers are supposed to consider every possibility at any time.{NOTE:研究者はどんなときでもあらゆるパターンを想定しておくものだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:41.00,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:936623,941003}Even when they lose their motivation and get depressed.{NOTE:たとえやる気を失い落ち込んだときであろうともな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:54.14,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:951805,954141}It's no use. I can't even graze him!{NOTE:駄目だ。まったく歯が立たん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:57.18,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,{TIME:954141,957186}But the town is done for unless we stop it!{NOTE:でも俺たちが止めなければ街が危ない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:59.81,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:957186,959813}No need to worry! Leave it to Navirou!{NOTE:大丈夫だ！ナビルーたちに任せろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.15,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:961648,963150}Hurry up and stop it!{NOTE:早く止めるんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.19,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:963150,964193}Manelger!{NOTE:マネルガー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.15,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:964193,965152}Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:08.15,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:965152,968155}I don't take instructions from the likes of you.{NOTE:私はお前らの指図など受けん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:12.45,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:968155,972451}Researchers work at their own pace, with their own will, and spirit of inquiry.{NOTE:研究者とは自分の意志と探究心のみで動く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.32,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:972451,974328}That's our Doctor!{NOTE:よっ！さすが博士。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:17.49,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:974328,977498}Fine, fine, but could he hurry up?{NOTE:何でもいいから早くやってくれるかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.58,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:977498,978582}Hmm…{NOTE:ふむ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.21,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:982336,984213}Doctor, what did you do?{NOTE:は、博士、どうしました？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:31.47,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:985214,991470}After careful consideration, this is reusing an abandoned research product.{NOTE:よく考えるとこれは過去に捨て去った研究作品を再度使用すること。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:34.55,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:991887,994556}In other words, this isn't a challenge.{NOTE:つまり、これはチャレンジではない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.68,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:994556,995682}Huh!?{NOTE:はあ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:38.60,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:995682,998602}I don't understand what you're getting at!{NOTE:いまさら何訳の分からんことを言ってるんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:40.06,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:998602,1000062}Just stop the monster already!{NOTE:取りあえず止めろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:42.23,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000062,1002231}Yes! And undo the modification.{NOTE:そうよ！そして改造を…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.77,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002231,1004775}Make it like it was before-nyaa.{NOTE:元に戻してあげてでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:48.15,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004775,1008153}You're the only one who can do it.{NOTE:それができるのはあなたしかいないのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.53,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008153,1009530}Hey! Manelger!{NOTE:おい！マネルガー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:51.36,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009530,1011365}Can you do it? Or is it too difficult?{NOTE:やるのかやらないのか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.78,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011365,1012783}Hmm…{NOTE:う～む…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:57.99,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017412,1017996}Eh?{NOTE:えっ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.41,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017996,1019414}Wha-aaat!?{NOTE:ええ～!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.45,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019414,1021458}Hey, what was that about?!{NOTE:おい、何やってるんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:05.67,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021458,1025671}Reusing past research projects is retrograde.{NOTE:やはり過去のものを使うということは研究の逆行。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.88,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025671,1027881}In other words, it's regression.{NOTE:つまり後退を意味する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.80,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027881,1030801}Something researcher's pride won't forgive!{NOTE:研究者としてのプライドが許さない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:14.01,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030801,1034012}Nobody cares about your pride!{NOTE:あなたのプライドとかどうでもいいから！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:18.05,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035180,1038058}The modified Tigrex has noticed us!{NOTE:大変だ！改造ティガレックスが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:22.35,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039560,1042354}Fine, it looks like we're the only ones who can stop it!{NOTE:こうなったらナビルーたちで止めるしかない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.94,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042354,1044940}I won't let you go anywhere with my flames!{NOTE:俺の炎でこの先は行かせない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:31.94,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050320,1051947}Po-poppo-poop!{NOTE:プッ・プップ・プ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:33.24,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051947,1053240}Over here, over here!{NOTE:こっち、こっち！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:36.32,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053240,1056326}Navirou's donuts-smelling farts!{NOTE:ナビルーのおならはドーナツの香り！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.49,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056326,1058495}Fart navigation! Come on!{NOTE:おならナビで、ほら、おいで！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.37,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064626,1065377}Eh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:49.17,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065377,1069172}Why does the remodeled Tigrex react to his fart?{NOTE:何であいつのおならに改造ティガレックスが？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:51.50,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069172,1071508}Everyone loves donuts!{NOTE:ドーナツはみ～んな大好きなのだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:57.18,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075262,1077180}Please leave it to me.{NOTE:ここは僕に任せてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.02,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085272,1087024}And next up is me!{NOTE:次は私よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:09.06,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087024,1089067}Kira-kira-nyaa!{NOTE:キラキラニャ～ン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:15.94,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094948,1095949}Alright, Floof!{NOTE:よし、チャモ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.49,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095949,1097492}Now's your turn!{NOTE:今だゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.07,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097492,1099077}Got it-nyaa.{NOTE:分かったでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.83,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108003,1109838}It felt asleep nicely.{NOTE:無事眠ったゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.17,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109838,1111173}We did it!{NOTE:やったぞー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:31.92,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111173,1111923}All right!{NOTE:これぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:34.00,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111923,1114009}United as always!{NOTE:いつだって心は一つ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.59,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114009,1116595}We're… the Numbers!{NOTE:俺たち…ナンバーズ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.60,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118680,1121600}This… is something that research can't do.{NOTE:こ…これぞ研究ではつくれない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.35,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121600,1123352}The power of friendship!{NOTE:友情の力。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.18,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123935,1126188}Manelger, do us a favor.{NOTE:マネルガー、お願いだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:49.44,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126188,1129441}Turn that modified Tigrex back to the way it was.{NOTE:あの改造ティガレックスを元に戻してやってくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.02,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129441,1132027}It's enough…{NOTE:改造されたままでいるのは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:54.19,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132027,1134196}…if we're the only ones modified.{NOTE:僕たちだけで十分です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.36,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134196,1136365}I fully agree.{NOTE:ええ。そのとおりよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:58.03,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136365,1138033}Please.{NOTE:頼むゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.45,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138033,1139451}Please-nyaa.{NOTE:お願いでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.11,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139785,1141119}Hmm…{NOTE:ふむ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.20,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141119,1142204}Doctor?{NOTE:博士。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.66,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142204,1143664}Very well.{NOTE:分かっている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.12,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143664,1145123}Let's restore it.{NOTE:元に戻そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.24,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145123,1146249}Really!?{NOTE:本当か!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:09.71,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146249,1149711}It's not like I'm doing this because you asked me to!{NOTE:別にお前らに頼まれたからではない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:15.75,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149711,1155759}I heard there's a group called the Ebon Riders\Nwandering about these days.{NOTE:噂によると近ごろﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞというやからがうろうろしているらしいな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.13,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155759,1157135}Wait, you really knew…?{NOTE:知っていたのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.92,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157135,1158929}About the Ebon Riders.{NOTE:ﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞのことを。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:20.43,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158929,1160430}Of course I did.{NOTE:当たり前だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:26.72,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160430,1166728}But they weren't very interesting,\Nso I didn't focus on them in my research.{NOTE:しかしそんなやつらは私の研究の足元にも及ばないし興味もない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:35.19,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166728,1175195}But it'll be pretty troublesome if such shady characters got to use my modified monsters.{NOTE:だがそんなどこの馬の骨とも分からんやつらに私の作った改造モンスターを利用されでもしたら困る。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.94,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175195,1177948}And that's why I'm restoring it.{NOTE:だから元に戻すのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.30,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204808,1206309}I'm glad.{NOTE:よかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:09.60,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206309,1209604}The Tigrex is better off in that form.{NOTE:ティガレックスはやっぱりあの姿の方がいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:12.94,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209604,1212941}Then let's restore you guys as well.{NOTE:なら、お前らも元に戻してやろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.10,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212941,1214109}What did you say!?{NOTE:何だと!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.19,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214109,1215193}In short…{NOTE:つまり…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:21.11,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215193,1221116}Let's turn you all back to how you were before the modification.{NOTE:ナンバーズの皆さんを改造前の姿に戻してあげましょう。ということで～す！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:23.70,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221116,1223702}Hey! I wanted to say it!{NOTE:…ってそれは私のせりふだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.45,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223702,1225454}Oh, I'm so glad.{NOTE:ああ～、よかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.03,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225454,1227038}That's my usual Doctor.{NOTE:これぞいつもの博士。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.25,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228331,1230250}I refuse.{NOTE:そういうことなら断る。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:31.16,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230250,1231168}Why?{NOTE:なぬ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.00,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231168,1232002}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.46,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232002,1233462}Are you sure?{NOTE:断っちゃうんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.84,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234755,1237841}Navirou likes how he is.{NOTE:ナビルーは今のナビルーが好きだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:38.88,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237841,1238884}Yes.{NOTE:ええ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.88,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238884,1240886}I like my current form as well.{NOTE:僕も今の自分が好きです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:42.30,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240886,1242304}I do, too.{NOTE:私も。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:46.72,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242304,1246725}We owe it to the Doctor that the six of us met.{NOTE:こうして俺たち６人が会えたのも博士がいたおかげだしな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:48.81,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246725,1248810}Precisely.{NOTE:そのとおりゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:53.52,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248810,1253523}Mille-Mille says she loves the current Floof, too.{NOTE:ミルミルも今のチャモを大好きって言ってくれるでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:55.73,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253523,1255734}So I'm good with this form-nyaa.{NOTE:だからこのままがいいでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.48,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256151,1257486}Hmm?{NOTE:ふ～ん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:01.86,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258445,1261865}Just kidding! You can't be restored either way.{NOTE:な～んて、本当はもう元には戻せんがな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:05.49,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261865,1265494}But I can always modify you further to make you cooler.{NOTE:だが、もっとカッコ良く改造することならできるぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:06.74,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265994,1266745}Hey!{NOTE:おい！}
